h Linux Simons Foundation is an Equal Opportunity Employer, M/F/D/V. C++, Python, MySql, Postgres, Linux, Mongo, Hadoop, Java, Data Mining/Modeling Apply Here PI93389387 More / Less How to apply Apply Here More / Less Location Manhattan, NY, 10010, US More / Less Details Start date April 6, 2016 Application deadline June 6, 2016 Education requirements 4-year degree Employment type Full time Professional level None specified Job function Technology Owner's areas of focus Media , Philanthropy , Network of nonprofits , Research and science More / Less Map More / Less Get career tips from our experts Half the Sky Appears: A Double-Book Review posted 3 days ago 3 Ways to Bring Joy to Your Job Search posted 6 days ago Should I Resend my Re-done Resume? posted 17 days ago 5 Entrepreneurial Techniques to Drive Your Nonprofit Career posted 20 days ago Without Fail: How Learning From Mistakes Leads to Success posted 24 days ago About History Our Team Working Here Learn Nonprofit Careers Volunteering Volunteering Abroad Grad School Attend Idealist Grad Fairs linkedin twitter facebook youtube Terms and Conditions | Privacy Policy | Community Guidelines © 1995- 2016 , Action Without Borders Idealist.org by Idealist.org is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivs 3.0 Unported License . Based on a work at www.idealist.org . Permissions beyond the scope of this license may be available at http://www.idealist.org . close Email Facebook Twitter Social Sharing by Janrain Share with Your Friends By Email Email sent Thanks for sharing with your contacts via email. Share with your other networks too! Start Over Select your contacts x + 11 Edit Done Close Done Selected contacts x + 11 Edit Done Close Done x + 30 Edit Done or browse contacts and 0 more x + It appears the URL has been modified. Restore? -56 Edit Done x + -155 Edit Done Job (Manhattan): Senior Software Engineer - idealist.org http://www.idealist.org/step/discover/share/jr/view/job/6N4tPXMNkNH4?utm